NPM:Node Package Manager
查看版本:npm -v

NRM:npm registry manager
安装:
    Windows:npm install -g nrm
    Mac:sudo npm install -g nrm
作用:
    NRM是NPM镜像源的管理工具，可以通过NRM在NPM源之间进行切换，找到当前最快的源进行安装

PS C:\project\sample> nrm ls

  npm ---------- https://registry.npmjs.org/
  yarn --------- https://registry.yarnpkg.com/
  tencent ------ https://mirrors.cloud.tencent.com/npm/
  cnpm --------- https://r.cnpmjs.org/
  taobao ------- https://registry.npmmirror.com/
  npmMirror ---- https://skimdb.npmjs.com/registry/

PS C:\project\sample> nrm test

* npm ------ 666ms
  yarn ----- 1164ms
  tencent -- 2027ms
  cnpm ----- 547ms
  taobao --- 815ms
  npmMirror - 2288ms

PS C:\project\sample> nrm test npm

* npm ------ 89ms

PS C:\project\sample> nrm test yarn

  yarn ----- 694ms

PS C:\project\sample> nrm test taobao

  taobao --- 526ms

PS C:\project\sample> nrm use npm


   Registry has been set to: https://registry.npmjs.org/

PS C:\project\sample> nrm use yarn


   Registry has been set to: https://registry.yarnpkg.com/

构建开发环境
1.npm install -g imooc-es-cli

2.imooc-es-cli -h 查看当前命令包括哪些可以使用的命令

3.imooc-es-cli init 初始化
? Project name: es-demo
New project has been initialized successfully!

4.npm install 安装项目所依赖的包

5.npm run start 启动项目

6.访问localhost:8080






